+/**
+ * drm_gpusvm_range_get_pages() - Get pages for a GPU SVM range
+ * @gpusvm: Pointer to the GPU SVM structure
+ * @range: Pointer to the GPU SVM range structure
+ * @ctx: GPU SVM context
